  "instructions": [
    "Heat sunflower oil in a large non-stick pan over medium-high heat",
    "Add lamb mince and cook until browned, breaking up with a spoon as it cooks",
    "Mince garlic and grate ginger; add to pan and cook until fragrant",
    "Add lamb's liver (if using) and cook until browned",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together honey, apple cider vinegar, and chilli flakes to make the glaze",
    "Brush the glaze over the lamb during the last 2 minutes of cooking",
    "Season with black pepper to taste",
    "Divide the cooked lamb among toasted buns and garnish with parsley"
